        "subject": "LU-4014 autoconf: Configure debuginfo/symbol stripping",
        "message": "LU-4014 autoconf: Configure debuginfo/symbol stripping\n\nCurrently, Lustre uses the system defaults for the RPM macros which\ncontrol whether a separate debuginfo RPM is created and symbols ae\nstripped from the KO files.\n\nSo currently, to control this behavior, the system/user defaults for\nRPM macros must be changed.  This patch makes those macros\nconfigurable for just Lustre as part of the build process.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I9fbfae0006067340bc983993d79fdfd692eb405f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
